<TEXT>
peter guertler the owner of viennas 
most famous hotel and former husband of onetime us ambassador 
helene von damm has committed suicide police say 
guertler 44 shot himself to death in his hunting lodge 
wednesday in pernitz 30 miles south of vienna police said they 
did not say whether he had left a suicide note and they did not 
provide further details 
ms von damm was guertlers second wife they married while she 
was ambassador in 1985 and she resigned a few months later citing 
an appearance of conflict of interest 
the couple was divorced less than two years later and guertler 
remarried 
guertler owned two topclass vienna hotels including the hotel 
sacher famous for the sacher torte the delicately flavored 
chocolate cake the hotel began producing about 100 years ago 
</TEXT>
