leuchter a resident of malden a northern suburb of boston 
designs and builds death machinery for states that allow capital 
punishment including tennessee new jersey delaware illinois and 
missouri 
he drew fire after writing a report claiming that gas chambers 
at some death camps couldnt have been used to kill hundreds of 
thousands of prisoners the report has been used as ammunition by 
some antisemitic groups 
