had destroyed schools pillaged museums and stolen archives since 
the aug 2 invasion 
iraqs delegate aziz al hajj ali haidar described the 
allegations as lies or rumors and protested the politicization 
of unesco he said items had been moved from museums to be stored 
safely in the event of bombardments 
