peace prize when his country had supplied arms and military 
advisers to iraq 
the soviet union has since denounced iraq for invading kuwait 
but it has not provided soldiers to stand beside us forces 
opposing baghdad 
sakharov a physicist and human rights activists was awarded 
the nobel award in 1975 soviet officials did not allow him to come 
to oslo for the prize that year ut he picked it up last year 
shortly before his death 
bonner who was in oslo to promote a norwegian edition of 
