the citys waikiki resort area was an ideal test site because of 
the large number of japanese tourists cook said glacier ice 
became a popular novelty item in japan a couple years ago 
glacier ice compressed over thousands of years has a clear 
prismlike sparkle and is denser than ice produced by refrigerators 
or ice machines cook said 
the density means it melts more slowly and doesnt water down 
drinks as quickly as regular ice cubes he said 
the product has been well received by customers who say it 
doesnt change the taste of their drinks said sean ellis food and 
