spend the day drumming up gop support for the measure 
the plan would raise taxes on cigarettes and luxury items and 
force spending cuts for a variety of federal programs but the 
democrats no longer are insisting on imposing a surtax on the rich 
rather foley said the new plan fully supplants the impact of 
the surtax 
