legislation on topics as diverse as the drug war environmental 
protection the military budget and privacy of genetic information 
he sponsored legislation which became law this year requiring 
the fbi to compile statistics on crimes motivated by bigotry 
another conyers bill that would register people to vote when they 
obtain a drivers license has cleared the house 
