could hold some surprises 
theres clearly a pretty strong sense of anger out among the 
voters and it is directed both at politics and politicians as much 
as incumbents said geoff garin a pollster with the democratic 
firm of peter hart 
there is a sense that people in government only care about 
politics and not about whats right and wrong he said 
