198182 version which involved a precipitous drop into a black 
hole 
the partial information that is now available for the third 
quarter together with some major work stoppages the crisis in the 
middle east and the weakening us economy suggest a further 
decline in output wilson said however we do not expect this 
to be a severe recession 
